This paper is primarily focused on video action recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses pre-training and transfer learning, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of hashtags and social media videos, which could be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories.
